NEW FILE, usb_programs/user_readme.txt, CREATED. CONTENTS:

WELCOME:

Run "python usb_main.py" to start.
Run "python usb_main.py help" for help.

Alternatively, run the individual programs. Here are the operations and their corresponding programs:

"python usb_main.py help" = "python help.py" 
"python usb_main.py create" = "python create.py" 
"python usb_main.py info" = "python info.py" 
"python usb_main.py reg" = "python reg.py" 
"python usb_main.py gen" = "python gen_crypt_data.py" 
"python usb_main.py newpass" = "python change_password.py" 
"python usb_main.py login" = "python login.py" 
"python usb_main.py logout" = "python logout.py" 